 (Video Source: Youtube)  A video titled “Virus Spreader” was posted on social media platforms overseas on Friday. The video, edited by some Chinese netizens, shows how the U.S. has exported COVID-19 virus at the expense of the lives and health of people of other countries. Click the video and take a look at how the U.S., which boasts of being the "beacon of civilization" on the globe, has deteriorated into a "super spreader" of COVID-19 virus, damaging the rights and interests of the people around the world.   